19369/43120 block mod_2 op 300_washer dcr
turn_off main_city water_fill line
with power on and machine in manual
pump will_engage and drain tank_automatically
keep_a close_eye that the pump be keep_up with flow_come out of tank
once tank be drain close drain valve
unlock_door from panel
open robot door at back of wet_station note no_other door be to be open_during cleaning
power_down machine at control_panel by_main disconnect
follow the lockout_map for proper_lockout
have_trade remove the plexglass_guard from the dirty tank
begin clean filter tank only
once clean tank be empty_please reach_below pump in tank
next_area to clean be the washer_wet room_enter through the pump room door
first_let 's_talk about_what -PRON- be not go to clean
please_wash all_four wall and the floor
remove_any chip_that be in the washing_room

with power on and machine in manual

pump will_engage and drain tank_automatically
please clean the lens on the machine_lighting in the room
clean the round_window and remove_any dry_solution off of the glass
remove_any chip_that be in the washing_room
please_wash all_four wall and the floor
first_let 's_talk about_what -PRON- be not go to clean

once clean tank be empty_please reach_below pump in tank
begin clean filter tank only
have_trade remove the plexglass_guard from the dirty tank
follow the lockout_map for proper_lockout
power_down machine at control_panel by_main disconnect
please clean the lens on the machine_lighting in the room
please_wash the screen in_front of the drain_locate on the back_wall
remove_any chip_that be in the washing_room
please_wash all_four wall and the floor
clean the next_station which be the robot dry station
important_only if_heating element be to be replace next_step
please_wash the screen in_front of the drain_locate on the back_wall
test machine in auto
power_up machine at control_panel
insure_that air be turn on and city_water valve be turn back on
prod_tl insure_that all lock have be remove
clean the round_window and remove_any dry_solution off of the glass
remove all safety lock as all inside work have_now be complete
final_cleaning

unlock_door from panel
once tank be drain close drain valve
keep_a close_eye that the pump be keep_up with flow_come out of tank
pump will_engage and drain tank_automatically
with power on and machine in manual
turn_off main_city water_fill line
production_tl to prep_washer for system cleaning
turn conveyor before washer to manual to empty out washer
first_let 's_talk about_what -PRON- be not go to clean
next_area to clean be the washer_wet room_enter through the pump room door
power_up machine at control_panel
please_wash all_four wall and the floor
insure_that air be turn on and city_water valve be turn back on
prod_tl insure_that all lock have be remove
conatact_production tl and inform_that -PRON- have remove all lock
remove all safety lock as all inside work have_now be complete
final_cleaning
reinstall_floor grate_back inside pump room
clean the round_window and remove_any dry_solution off of the glass
please clean the lens on the machine_lighting in the room
please_wash the screen in_front of the drain_locate on the back_wall
